Come on, baby!

01:30:32.733 --> 01:30:34.035
Come on, baby!

01:30:34.969 --> 01:30:36.537
Come on!

01:30:38.506 --> 01:30:40.074
Come on! Do your best!

01:30:40.107 --> 01:30:42.209
Come on, that's it.

01:30:42.243 --> 01:30:44.111
- Come on.
